{"tid":1972464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關心不能算干……預！……中央的關心，能算干預麼","createTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T11:07:49.000Z","uid":24660,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f78f2f5b1e967fb0072da1140b3a5d10cac75c4","tid":1972464,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭一到演講廳，所有記者便都看著她笑，有的叫道，「林鄭，港澳辦中聯辦發文譴責郭榮鏗了！」她不回答，對鏡頭說，「保就業計劃，要財委會審議通過撥款。」便排出九千大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「港澳辦中聯辦干預香港了！」林鄭睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白?我前天親眼見港澳辦中聯辦譴責郭榮鏗濫權，嚴重干擾立法會內部正常運作。」林鄭便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「關心不能算干&hellip;&hellip;預！&hellip;&hellip;中央的關心，能算干預麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「鐵證如山」，什麼「不容抵賴」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：演講廳內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"f4b7ce817c65c6ad3135e8693e9906fd9fc1f523","tid":1972464,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"即係同條女講, 我強行插入, 唔算 強.... 姦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823b899962a2f5e7af58eefac01a51760703199c","tid":1972464,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"充滿病毒的空氣就有"},{"pid":"3e6c9b58b95b6597268e7278e86129b30ae7063f","tid":1972464,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4b7ce817c65c6ad3135e8693e9906fd9fc1f523","tid":1972464,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"即係同條女講, 我強行插入, 唔算 強.... 姦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.